          "highlight": [
            "embarrassed"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "她在會議中忘記了同事的名字，感到十分難為情。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "He was clearly embarrassed by the unexpected compliment from his boss.",
          "highlight": [
            "embarrassed"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "他顯然對主管突如其來的稱讚感到窘迫。"
          }
        }
